==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unpen
<hw>Un*pen"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>pen</ets>.]</ety> <def>To release from a pen or
from confinement.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧If a man <xex>unpens</xex> another's
water.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpenetrable</ent>⟦br⟧
